videos.headline: Cincy RB fights through defense for the score
videos.description: Michael Warren II runs past several defenders and scores from 8 yards out to put Cincinnati on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincy RB fights through defense for the score) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincy QB throws a dime for 4th-down TD
videos.description: On fourth down, Desmond Ridder lofts a perfect pass to Josiah Deguara in the end zone for a 27-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincy QB throws a dime for 4th-down TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincy extends lead with 51-yard TD toss
videos.description: Desmond Ridder airs it out to Thomas Geddis deep down the sideline for a 51-yard Cincinnati touchdown.
